ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
Subject(Wheat, red winter wheat, amber durum wheat, feed barley and designated barley) Freight Adjustment Factors ** APPROVAL THEREOF **
PrecisOrder approving the amounts established by the Canadian Wheat Board of the FREIGHT ADJUSTMENT FACTORS for certain delivery points for WHEAT, RED WINTER WHEAT, AMBER DURUM WHEAT, FEED BARLEY and DESIGNATED BARLEY to be delivered to The Canadian Wheat Board during the 2010-2011 pool period, beginning August 1, 2010.
